The paper deals with foreground object detection, which is a common problem in computer vision. The proposed solution involves combining different background subtraction algorithms using a convolutional neural network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) category. Additionally, the use of a neural network indicates that the paper may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The evaluation of the proposed method on a dataset suggests that the paper may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
